The My Own Magazine Archive is a collection of correspondence, manuscripts, and issues of the magazine, edited by Jeff Nuttall. This archive also incorporates the magazine The Moving Times, edited by William Burroughs.

abstract.value: The My Own Magazine Archive contains correspondence and submissions made to the editor, Jeff Nuttall. Submissions included are manuscripts from William Burroughs, Robert Creeley, Lawrence Ferlinghetti, and Allen Ginsberg. This collection also incorporates The Moving Times, a magazine edited by William Burroughs.
